  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 425°F (220°C).",
    "Toss the daikon radish slices with olive oil, salt, and crushed red pepper flakes on a baking sheet.",
    "Roast in the preheated oven for 20 minutes, or until the daikon is tender and caramelized.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together mustard seeds, garlic, and lemon juice.",
    "Once the daikon is done, toss it with the mustard mixture and chopped parsley.",
    "Serve hot, topped with crumbled feta cheese if desired.",
    "Garnish with additional parsley if desired.",
    "Serve immediately, and enjoy!"
